article.description: — Baylor Scheierman had a career-high 23 points as South Dakota State defeated Utah State 83-59 on Thursday night in the Bad Boy Mowers Crossover Classic.
article.headline: Scheierman leads South Dakota State past Utah State 83-59
article.linkText: Scheierman leads South Dakota State past Utah State 83-59
article.story: SIOUX FALLS, S.D. -- — Baylor Scheierman had a career-high 23 points as South Dakota State defeated Utah State 83-59 on Thursday night in the Bad Boy Mowers Crossover Classic. Douglas Wilson had 16 points and Alex Arians added 13 points for South Dakota State (1-1). David Wingett had 11 points. Neemias Queta had 12 points, three assists and three blocks for the Aggies (0-2). Marco Anthony added 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
